quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Kaaf. M wẽen ne Alkʋrãan-zɩsgã."
  50,2,"Pa woto ye, b maana yel-solemd ne bugsd sẽn wa bãmb nengẽ sẽn yi bãmb pʋgẽ; tɩ kɩfr-dãmb yeele: ""yãoã yaa yel-solemd tɛkẽ""."
  50,3,"Rẽ yĩnga tõnd sã n ki n lebg tom, ad rẽnda yaa lεbeng sẽn zãre."
  50,4,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd bãnga Tẽngã sẽn boogd bãmbã, la Tõnd tara gaf sẽn gũus bũmbɑ fãɑ."
  50,5,"Pa woto ye, b yagsa sɩdã a sẽn wa n wa bãmb nengẽ, tɩ bãmb be yel-gẽdem pʋga."
  50,6,"Yalla bãmb pa get n tʋg saagã bãmb zugẽ wã, wãn-wãn la Tõnd me-a la D nags-a, t'a pa tar pãrgre?"
  50,7,"La tẽn-gãongã, Tõnd yadg-a lame la D tilg tãms a zugu; la D buls a zugã (bõn-yitim) kõbg fãa gill sẽn be neere."
  50,8,"Tɩ yaa tags-n-gɛsg la tẽegr ne yamb fãa sẽn yaa lebs-m-meng soaba."
  50,9,"La Tõnd sika saagẽ wã koom sẽn tar barka, tɩ Tõnd bulsd ne-a pʋt la bõn-bεεl sẽn kẽebde."
  50,10,"La tamar tɩɩsã sẽn yɑɑ wogd n tar gĩna."
  50,11,"Yaa rɩtl ne yembsã, la D leb n vɩɩms ne-a tẽn-kɩɩnga, la woto bal la yiibã (vʋʋgrã)"
  50,12,"La rɑ reng n yɑgsɑ tɑoor tɩ bãmb pɑ wɑ, a Nuuh nebã la Raas bulg rãmbɑ la a -Ṯamuud rãmbã."
  50,13,"La a ʿAad rãmb la a Fɩr-aoon la a Lʋʋt saam-biisã."
  50,14,"La Ayka rãmba (ti-gũmdɩ) la Tʋbba nebã, b fãa gill yagsa Tẽn-tʋʋmbã, tɩ Mam pʋlen-wẽngã yɩ sɩda b zugu."
  50,15,"Rẽ yĩnga Tõnd konga pãng rẽenem naanegã sasa? Pa woto ye, b bee sik pʋg ne naaneg paalle bãmb kũumɑ poorẽ."
  50,16,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd naana ninsaala, la d mi bũmb ning a yõorã sẽn liibd-a ne wã, la Tõnd n pẽ-a n yɩɩd kokor gĩindi."
  50,17,"Wakat ning Mɑlεk koakdb a yiibã sã n wa kokd ɑ tʋʋmã, n zĩ ɑ rɩtg wεεngẽ la ɑ goabg wεεngẽ."
  50,18,"A pa be sẽn na yeel gomde, rẽndame tɩ gũusd n sεgl a meng n be a zugu."
  50,19,"Tɩ kũumã vẽsbã wa ne sɩda, rẽnda la bũmb ning fo sẽn da lakd n basdẽ wã."
  50,20,"Tɩ b fʋʋs Baorgã, yaa rẽnda la pʋlen-wẽng raare."
  50,21,"Tɩ yõor fãa wa, ne a pεεgd la a sεεta."
  50,22,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka fo ra bee yam yaal-yaal pʋgẽ, tɩ Tõnd pãrg fo fu-goabgã n bas-fo, tɩ fo nifã noom rũndã raarã."
  50,23,"T'a tũud-n-taagã (malεk ning sẽn gũusd a tʋʋmã) yeele: ""wãnda la bũmb ning sẽn be mam nengẽ, yaa sẽn segl n sε""."
  50,24,"Lob-y Gεhanm pʋgẽ kɩfr toaag fãa sẽn yaa ko-kor kεgeng soaba."
  50,25,"N yaa sõma gɩdg toog soaba, n yaa maan-n-zʋʋg soaba, n yaa sik maanda."
  50,26,"Sẽn maan-a soaben-zẽng n lagem Wẽnde; bɩ a lob-a naong kεgengã pʋgẽ."
  50,27,"T'a tũud-n-taagã (a Sʋɩtãan) yeele: ""yaa tõnd Soaba, mam pa mɑɑn-ɑ tɑ kedg ye, la bala a ra yɩ n bee meneng sẽn zãr pʋgẽ""."
  50,28,"T'A (Wẽnd) yeele: ""ra zab-y taab Mam taoor ye, tɩ sɩd la hakɩɩka M da lʋɩɩsa taoor yãmb nengẽ pʋlen-wẽnga,"
  50,29,"Gomd pa tedgd Mam nengẽ ye, la Mam pa yɩ n yaa wẽgd bɑɑ fʋɩ ne yembsã ye."
  50,30,"Raar ning Tõnd sẽn yet Gεhamn:"" f pidame bɩ?"" t'a yeele: ""sẽn paasd beeme bɩ?"""
  50,31,"Tɩ b pẽneg Arzãn ne wẽn-zoetbã, tɩ pa zãr ye."
  50,32,"Woto la b sẽn pʋlem yãmba, lebs-m-meng soab fãa sẽn yaa gũus-m-meng soab fãa yĩnga."
  50,33,"Ned ning sẽn zoe-a Arrahmaan Naaba ne a sẽn pa ne-A wã fãa, la a wa ne sũur sẽn yaa lebs-m-meng soab sũuri."
  50,34,"Kẽ-y-yã-a ne tɩlgre, rẽnda yaa duung raare."
  50,35,"Be ne bãmba, bũmb ning b sẽn tʋll a pʋgẽ, la paasg be Tõnd nengẽ."
  50,36,"La sõor waoog Tõnd sẽn halk bãmb taoor sẽn yaa zãma, tɩ b pãng keelem yɩɩd bãmbã? Tɩ b yi n sa tẽmsã, yalla põsg zĩig beemẽ bɩ?"
  50,37,"Sɩd la hakɩɩka, ad tẽegr be rẽ pʋgẽ ne ned ning sẽn tar-a sũuri, ma t'a kɩll n kelg tɩ yẽ yaa sẽn ning ɑ toɑɑgɑ."
  50,38,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd naana saasã la Tẽngã, la bũmb ning sẽn be b yiibã sʋkã, rasem a yoob pʋgẽ, la yaams pa sɩɩs Tõnd ye."
  50,39,"Bɩ f maan sugri ne bũmb ning b sẽn yetã, la f yɩlg fo Soabã yʋʋre n pẽ-A lɑ f pʋʋs taoor tɩ wĩntoogã pa puki, la taoor t'a pa lʋɩ."
  50,40,"La yʋng bɩ f yɩlg-A, la suguud-rãmb poorẽ."
  50,41,"La tõog kelgre; raar ning boaandã sẽn na n wɑ peebdẽ n boond zĩig sẽn pẽ(pẽem pẽem)."
  50,42,"Raar ning b sẽn wʋmd kaasgã ne sɩdã, rẽ la yiibã raare."
  50,43,"Ad Tõndo, Tõnd n vɩɩmsd la D kʋʋda, baasg zĩig me yaa Tõnd nengẽ."
  50,44,"Raar ning Tẽngã sẽn pãrsd n basd-b ne yãgbo, rẽ yaa Tiging sẽn yaa naana ne Tõndo."
  50,45,"Tõnd n yɩɩd minim ne b sẽn yet bũmb ningã, la fo pa yɩ n yaa moadgd b zug ye, bɩ f tẽeg ne Alkʋrãanã ned ning sẽn yaεεsd-a Mam pʋlen-kẽengã."
